{"tid":2007100,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黨衛軍以行為不檢拘捕浸大記者","createTime":"2020-05-08T07:37:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T07:45:11.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"591d4102a65f6ef2eef5a84fbd3b328998c26a3d","tid":2007100,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T07:37:11.000Z","msg":"數十人在中環IFC集結　警方拘浸大編委記者<br />\n08.05.2020 15:16<br />\n<br />\n數十人下午在中環IFC商場聚集，多名警員進入商場拉起封鎖線，圍封商場中庭，截查多人，包括東區區議員曾健成等數人，被票控違反限聚令。一名浸大編委會記者被警方拘捕，指其涉嫌干犯公眾地方行為不檢，多名記者上前拍攝時，有警員施放胡椒噴劑，多人不適，由在場義務急救員治理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1286076&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1286076%26csid%3D261_341&d=ZKl1Acg0IOD8KmAOqHMUQBnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=1f2e85cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1286076&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"6b3bb51ec8c1784d897d950687dbb299c1c246ff","tid":2007100,"uid":108606,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T07:41:19.000Z","msg":"其實每次佢鳩告嗰啲罪，我覺得佢地都係講返自己，eg暴動、違反限聚令、行為不檢、非法集結、瘋狂駕駛等等"},{"pid":"c66be9fe0729d4569b1456ba6eb553c1c94b5ad9","tid":2007100,"uid":31185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T07:45:11.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}